BD_Crafter.description: Basic production building. Utilises nanoscale printing to make Products.

BD_DroneJunction_2x2.name: Rail Junction 2x2
BD_DroneJunction_2x2.description: Connection for Drone Rails. Allows spliting and expanding their paths.

BD_DroneLane_3_2x2.name: Rail Support 3 Lanes 2x2
BD_DroneLane_3_2x2.description: Connection for Drone Rails. Allows spliting and expanding their paths.

BD_DroneLane_5_2x2.name: Rail Support 5 Lanes 2x2
BD_DroneLane_5_2x2.description: Connection for Drone Rails. Allows spliting and expanding their paths.

BD_DroneMerger3To1_2x2.name: Rail Node 2x2
BD_DroneMerger3To1_2x2.description: Connection for Drone Rails. Allows spliting and expanding their paths.

BD_DroneMerger5To1_2x2.name: Big Rail Node 2x2
BD_DroneMerger5To1_2x2.description: Connection for Drone Rails. Allows spliting and expanding their paths.

BD_DroneJunction.name: Drone Junction
BD_DroneJunction.description: Connection for Drone Rails. Allows spliting and expanding their paths.

BD_DroneJunction_4.name: Rail Connector
BD_DroneJunction_4.description: Connection for Drone Rails. Allows spliting and expanding their paths.

BD_DroneLane_3.name: Multirail 3
BD_DroneLane_3.description: Connection for Drone Rails. Used to support long Rails. Can connect up to 3 Rails.

BD_DroneLane_5.name: Multirail 5
BD_DroneLane_5.description: Connection for Drone Rails. Used to support long Rails. Can connect up to 5 Rails.

BD_DroneMerger_3To1.name: Rail Modulator 3
BD_DroneMerger_3To1.description: Connection for Drone Rails. Allows spliting or merging up to 3 Rails.

BD_DroneMerger_5To1.name: Rail Modulator 5
BD_DroneMerger_5To1.description: Connection for Drone Rails. Allows spliting or merging up to 5 Rails.

BD_DronePole.name: Rail Support
BD_DronePole.description: Connection for Drone Rails. Used to support long Rails.

BD_DronePole_2x2.name: Rail Pole 2x2
BD_DronePole_2x2.description: Connection for Drone Rails. Used to support long Rails.

BD_DroneRailT1.name: Rail v.1
BD_DroneRailT1.description: Core component of the rail system. Allows drones to transport items between buildings. Transfers 120 Items per minute. Conducts electricity.

BD_DroneRailT2.name: Rail v.2
BD_DroneRailT2.description: Core component of the rail system. Allows drones to transport items between buildings. Transfers 240 Items per minute. Conducts electricity.

BD_DroneRailT3.name: Rail v.3
BD_DroneRailT3.description: Core component of the rail system. Allows drones to transport items between buildings. Transfers 480 Items per minute. Conducts electricity.

BD_Exporter.name: Orbital Cargo Launcher
BD_Exporter.description: Sends supplied items to Corporations. Each sent Product increases your Value and reputation with selected Corporation.

BD_Furnace.name: Furnace
BD_Furnace.description: Basic production building. Utilises heat to make Products.

BD_GasExtractor.name: Helium-3 Extractor
BD_GasExtractor.description: Used to extract Helium-3. Can be placed only on Helium-3 deposits.

BD_Hammer.name: Mega Press
BD_Hammer.description: Intermediate production building. Utilises high speed machining to make Products.

BD_Analyzer.name: Analyzing Station
BD_Analyzer.description: Used to analyze items in exchange for Data Points. Has to be placed inside a Habitat.

BD_Armory.name: Equipment Upgrade Station
BD_Armory.description: Used for weapon management. Unlocks new weapons, and mods in exchange for War Bonds. Has to be placed inside a Habitat.

BD_CloningBed.name: Regeneration Chamber
BD_CloningBed.description: Respawn point. One player can claim one Regeneration Chamber at a time. Can be used to change Characters. Has to be placed inside a Habitat.

BD_FoodProcessor.name: Food Station
BD_FoodProcessor.description: Converts raw consumables. Has to be placed inside a Habitat.

BD_ItemPrinter.name: Basic Item Printer
BD_ItemPrinter.description: Produces Building Materials and Ammo. Has to be placed inside a Habitat.

BD_PersonalStorage.name: Personal Storage
BD_PersonalStorage.description: Used to store items. Can be placed on a wall or ground. Has to be placed inside a Habitat.

BD_PersonalStorageBig.name: Large Personal Storage
BD_PersonalStorageBig.description: Used to store items. Can be placed on a wall or ground. Has to be placed inside a Habitat.

BD_RecipeTable.name: Recipe Station
BD_RecipeTable.description: Unlocks new production and food recipes. Has to be placed inside a Habitat.

BD_ResearchTerminal.name: Corpo Terminal
BD_ResearchTerminal.description: Used to claim rewards from Corporations. Allows spending Data Points. Can be placed on a wall or ceiling. Has to be placed inside a Habitat.

BD_SuitWorkshop.name: L.E.M. Station
BD_SuitWorkshop.description: Allows instalation of Limbistic Enchancement Membranes (LEMs). Has to be placed inside a Habitat.

BD_MechanicalDrill.name: Ore Excavator
BD_MechanicalDrill.description: Crucial during the early phase of the mission. Used to extract basic ores. Can be placed only on Titanium, Wolfram, and Calcium deposits.

BD_Airlock.name: Airlock
BD_Airlock.description: Allows access to Habitats. Has to be build on a Habitat wall.

BD_HorizontalBridge.name: Horizontal Connector
BD_HorizontalBridge.description: Connects 2 Habitats placed side by side. Has to be placed inside a Habitat.

BD_VerticalBridge.name: Vertical Connector
BD_VerticalBridge.description: Allows access to a Habitat placed on top of another Habitat. Has to be placed inside a Habitat.

BD_ViewportSingle.name: Viewport
BD_ViewportSingle.description: Transparent barrier that resembles a window. Has to be placed on a Habitat wall.

BD_HabitatBig.name: Large Habitat
BD_HabitatBig.description: Protects from external threats. Allows placement of interior structures. Needs Airlock to access.

BD_HabitatSmall.name: Habitat
BD_HabitatSmall.description: Protects from external threats. Allows placement of interior structures. Needs Airlock to access.

BD_Modular_PillarSupport.name: Pillar Support
BD_Modular_PillarSupport.description: Supports Platforms placed on top of it.

BD_Modular_BasePlatform.name: Supported Platform
BD_Modular_BasePlatform.description: Platform that can be placed on terrain.

BD_Modular_ConnectingPlatform.name: Platform
BD_Modular_ConnectingPlatform.description: Can be connected to other Platforms or placed on Pillar Supports.

BD_Walkway.name: Extendable walkway
BD_Walkway.description: Smooth ramp used to connect Platforms.

BD_PackageReceiver.name: Cargo Receiver
BD_PackageReceiver.description: Allows long distance transportation of selected items. Requires Cargo Dispatcher to operate.

BD_PackageSender.name: Cargo Dispatcher
BD_PackageSender.description: Allows long distance transportation of selected items. Requires Cargo Receiver to operate.

BD_ChemicalProcessor.name: Chemical Processor
BD_ChemicalProcessor.description: Creates new substances with chemical reactions

BD_SonicDrill.name: Sonic Drill
BD_SonicDrill.description: Not included in EA version of the game. Did you cheat?

BD_Refinery.name: Refinery
BD_Refinery.description: Refines raw Helium, Sulphur, and Powerium into Products.

BD_ResourceRedistributor.name: Storage Depot v.1
BD_ResourceRedistributor.description: Redistributes items evenly to all connected buildings. Can store up to 400 units of one selected item.

BD_Smelter.name: Smelter
BD_Smelter.description: Refines raw Titanium, Wolfram, and Calcium into Products.

BD_SolarPowerGenerator.name: Solar Generator v.1
BD_SolarPowerGenerator.description: Basic power generator. Creates energy using photovoltaic cells.

BD_SolarPowerGeneratorTier2.name: Solar Generator v.2
BD_SolarPowerGeneratorTier2.description: More advanced power generator. Creates energy using higher efficiency photovoltaic cells.

BD_Storage.name: Storage Depot v.2
BD_Storage.description: Redistributes items evenly to all connected buildings. Can store up to 1600 units of one selected item.

BD_StorageDepot.name: Expandable Storage
BD_StorageDepot.description: Redistributes items evenly to all connected buildings. Can store up to 1600 units of one selected item.  Can be expanded using more Power.

BD_Synthetizer.name: Compounder
BD_Synthetizer.description: Intermediate production building. Utilises chemical reactions to make Products.

BD_Teleporter.name: Teleporter
BD_Teleporter.description: Allows long distance travel between any two Teleporters.

BD_TurretTier1.name: Defense Turret
BD_TurretTier1.description: Defensive structure. Automatically aims and shoots at enemies. Requires Standard Ammo to work. Has to be supplied manually.

BD_TurretTier2.name: Defense Tower
BD_TurretTier2.description: Defensive structure. Automatically aims and shoots at enemies. Requires Standard Ammo to work. Can be resupplied by Drone Rails.

BD_UniversalStorage.name: Multistorage
BD_UniversalStorage.description: Stores excess items that can not be sent anywhere else.  Holds up to 2500 units. Can store multiple distinct items.

BD_WindPowerGenerator.name: Wind Turbine v.1
BD_WindPowerGenerator.description: Basic power generator. Converts wind into electric energy.

BD_WindPowerGeneratorTier2.name: Wind Turbine v.2
BD_WindPowerGeneratorTier2.description: More advanced power generator. Converts wind into electric energy with higher efficiency.
